summary: This mod adds a Frostbite Spider Companion in Breezehome named Princess.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a Frostbite Spider Companion in Breezehome named Princess.

Inspiration for this mod comes from my friend Chrissy: [url=http://forums.nexusmods.com/index.php?/user/1688282-chrissy-m/]Chrissy\'s Forum Profile[/url]

These pictures were taken with my ENB, found here: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/40456//?]Subtle ENB by Bill[/url]

If you liked this mod, please endorse!

Check out my other mods: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/users/4831711/?tb=mods&pUp=1]My Mods[/url]

Thanks for your time!
author: billmineface
